Coingecko pump tracker

Your time has come to win this game

Have you ever noticed the spike in price when coins get listed on CoinGecko? Buying after the listing can lead to crazy returns in a few hours (2x, 10x or even 50x). We have been using this simple trick for weeks, and now is your time to thrive. However, you have to get in quickly – the first ones will get the biggest slice of the cake.

This is why we created CoinGecko Pump Tracker. Our tool will automatically buy when any token from the BSC network is listed, following some parameters defined by you such as: take-profit, stop-loss among many others. Now, you have everything in your hands to be the first one to get in!

CoinMarketCap pump tracker

The new gold rush

Our tool works the same way in CoinMarketCap too, so you are more likely to catch several pumps that give absurd returns every day.

You don’t have to spend hours and hours in front of the computer looking for coin launches that may or may not have pumps. Set aside 5 minutes of your time, configure our tool and activate.

Have your day off to do other things while you participate in pumps automatically, being one of the first to buy!

frequently asked questions

This should answer the most generic questions. For more, feel free to reach out on Telegram.
What is BSC?

Binance Smart Chain (BSC) is a blockchain network built for running smart contract-based applications. BSC runs in parallel with Binance’s native Binance Chain (BC), which allows users to get the best of both worlds: the high transaction capacity of BC and the smart contract functionality of BSC.

The aim of the platform is to enable developers to build decentralized applications (DApps) and help users manage their digital assets cross-chain with low latency and large capacity.

Are the funds SAFU?

Yea! We will burn all liquidity when we launch the token. That is giving up ownership at its best. We don’t want any preferences here, everyone has the same chances.

Will it be on pancakeSwap v1 or v2?

Our token will be launched on PancakeSwap V2, so we will be using the best technology that we have available today.

What are the tokenomics?

We are going to launch $TRACK token with cutting edge tokenomics.

Name: Trackzer
Symbol: $TRACK
Initial Supply: 1.000.000.000.000.000 $TRACK
TAX: 8% (8% or higher slippage)

2% transaction fee redistributed to all existing holders;
5% transaction fee going into the LP (auto-generated LP);
1% transaction fee going into Binance Charity Wallet. Learn more here.

That makes a total of 8% fee on every transaction. This will improve security by making bot trading on Trackzer impossible and prevent important price movements by increasing the liquidity over time.

Trackzer will have the proper bases to start its exponential expansion.

Who are you?

We’ve been getting lots of team-related questions from the community about Trackzer: “Who is the team behind Trackzer?” “Did you really code this amazing Pump Tracker?”

Our team is made up primarily of tech enthusiasts: some of us are software programmers, graphic designers or marketing specialist, but we all have one thing in common; we’re passionate about cryptocurrency. We see the Binance Smart Chain as the future of crypto, and we’re very proud to be part of the movement to support the growth and value of this promising blockchain.

We’re 3 co-founders, but three brilliant individuals already joined our team to support our growth. More things to come soon!

Will you have pre-sale?
No, our token will be fair launch, we will make the contract available on Telegram group as soon as the countdown reaches zero, so everyone will have the same opportunity to buy.
Where do I find the contract?
The contract will be made available in our Telegram group when the countdown reaches zero, this is done to protect our investors against bots and snipers at launch.
How can I access the tool?
To get access to our tools, you have to hold a minimum of 1.000.000.000 $TRACK Tokens (0,0001% of total supply). We’ve fixed it to be accessible for most of our holders, but the more people will get in, the more this will represent a higher amount of BNB to invest. So try to get in early!
